      <title>运营商表示，让德国燃煤电厂保持备用状态成本太高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/keeping-back-up-german-coal-plants-is-too-costly-says-operator</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国一家燃煤电厂运营商警告说，按照该国监管机构的要求，让发电厂处于待机状态以帮助在未来几年保持供电是无利可图的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/keeping-back-up-german-coal-plants-is-too-costly-says-operator</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 17:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
